subject: Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Geno Hayes returned Matt Ryan’s third interception of the game for a 38-yard touchdown with 1 minute 10 seconds to play last night to help Florida State upset No. 2 Boston College, 27-17, ending the Eagles’ run at an unbeaten season and shaking up the Bowl Championship Series standings yet again.
